name: Cozy Double 2 min walk to subway 12 min Downtown
neighborhood_overview: Our property is close to restaurants, bakeries, ice cream parlor and minutes walk to public transportation to get you downtown Boston and access to all the attractions Boston has to offer.
description:
Nicely decorated for your comfort 2 comfy double beds in a large room with access to 2 nicely done bathrooms, living room and full kitchen. WiFi connection and cable television in the living room. Walk for coffee, restaurants and cafes. Minutes walk to public transportation will get you downtown in 13 minutes.

The space
Shared spaces include 2 full bathrooms, fully stocked kitchen, WiFi and comfortable shared living room.

Other things to note
1. THIS ROOM IS ON THE 3rd floor. -

2. ON street Parking is LIMITED if you DRIVE private parking may be an additional $10 a day so please reserve during busy season.
